{"tid":1586681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白衣人在內街被「私了」出來後大罵警方「無X用」","createTime":"2019-09-22T05:31:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T05:31:03.000Z","uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7122e8cb9413bc39ffd5dc98a45fb42b76391a87","tid":1586681,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T05:31:03.000Z","msg":"元朗入夜後，開始有部份白衣人走出來，去追打抗爭者。然而，部份勇武派抗爭者似乎也不太客氣，被白衣人追打後開始反擊。有部份抗爭者疑在內街自行「私了」白衣人，白衣人被打後，走出來指罵警員，用粗口面對面稱他們「無x用」。香港大學學生會校園電視拍到相關影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2019/09/baiyirenzaijiebeisilechuhoudajingfangxyong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2019%2F09%2Fbaiyirenzaijiebeisilechuhoudajingfangxyong%2F&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=eeb23a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2019/09/baiyirenzaijiebeisilechuhoudajingfangxyong/</a>"}]}